            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/782_step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>potatoes</strong> into wedges and then cut them in half lengthways</p>\r\n<p>Add them to a separate baking tray (use<strong> tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!) with a drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and mix well</p>\r\n<p>Place in the oven and cook for 25 min</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/782.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/782.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/782.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/782.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/782.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pan (preferably non-stick) with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>sage</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> and cook for 30 sec until crispy</p>\r\n<p>Set aside on a piece of kitchen paper to drain the excess oil</p>\r\n<p>Reserve the pan for later&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/782.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
