          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dice the <strong>onion</strong> and the <strong>garlic&nbsp;</strong>finely&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat and add the <strong>diced&nbsp;onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>\r\n<p>Cook for 5-6 min until softened</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>diced&nbsp;garlic</strong> and cook for a further 1-2 min</p>",
